# FUGEN SmartPay — Complete System Description & Summary

---

## 📌 1. System Overview

**FUGEN SmartPay** is a **School ID–Based Cashless Canteen Management System** developed as a Capstone Project for the **Future Generation Philippine International School (FGPIS)** in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia. The system replaces traditional cash-based canteen payments with a secure, QR code–based digital wallet solution, enabling students to make purchases using a pre-loaded points balance linked to their student ID.

The platform supports **automated balance tracking**, reduces waiting time during canteen transactions, minimizes cash handling errors, and provides **transparent transaction records** accessible only to authorized school personnel.

### Core Concepts

| Concept | Description |
|---|---|
| **Currency** | Points-based system (displayed as Points/Pts) |
| **Authentication** | Student ID QR Code + 4-Digit Passkey |
| **Credit/Debt Logic** | Students can go up to -500 points (credit limit); debts are auto-deducted from next top-up |
| **Real-Time Sync** | All platforms (web, mobile, student portal) stay synchronized via Socket.IO |

