## ✅ 15. Implemented Features Summary

- ✅ Multi-role login system (Admin + Student + Mobile POS)
- ✅ Student CRUD with auto-generated IDs and LRN-based passkeys
- ✅ QR code generation, download, print, and bulk PDF export
- ✅ Cashless canteen POS with QR scanning and quick purchase entry
- ✅ Points-based balance system with credit limit enforcement (-500 max)
- ✅ Real-time synchronization across all platforms (Socket.IO)
- ✅ Transaction history with categorization (TOPUP, PURCHASE, DEDUCTION, WITHDRAWAL, CREDIT)
- ✅ Daily and weekly statistics with data visualization (Recharts)
- ✅ Top-up reservation request system with notification workflow
- ✅ In-app notification inbox for students
- ✅ Cash management with manual override capability
- ✅ Automated daily report saving (3:30 PM auto-save)
- ✅ Bulk import (CSV) and data export functionality
- ✅ Audit logging for admin actions
- ✅ Desktop application via Electron
- ✅ Cloud deployment (Render.com)
- ✅ Session persistence with timeout (24-hour web, AsyncStorage mobile)
- ✅ Account lockout after 5 failed passkey attempts
- ✅ bcrypt password hashing for security
- ✅ Atomic Firestore transactions for financial operations
- ✅ Responsive, professional UI/UX design

